{{Doomwiki}}Deathkings of the Dark Citadel ({{dw|HEXDD.WAD}}) is the official expansion pack for [[Hexen]]. Unlike The Ultimate Doom and Heretic: Shadow of the Serpent Riders, it was published as a commercial product and cannot be downloaded as a free upgrade. When released, it lacked the [[SNDINFO]] lump which associated [[MUS]] tracks to the maps; this was fixed by the 1.1 patch.
